<paragraph id="IFRS16_15" base="F45928996"><paranum>15</paranum><prolog><data name="standard_number" value="IFRS 16"/><data name="paranum" value="15"/></prolog><body><p id="IFRS16_P0052">As a practical expedient, a <xref base="F45929736" href="IFRS16_APPA.dita#IFRS16_APPA/IFRS16_P0380">lessee<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0220"/></ph></xref> may elect, by class of <xref base="F45929849" href="IFRS16_APPA.dita#IFRS16_APPA/IFRS16_P0392">underlying asset<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0373"/></ph></xref>, not to separate non-lease components from <xref base="F45929685" href="IFRS16_APPA.dita#IFRS16_APPA/IFRS16_P0363">lease<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0214"/></ph></xref> components, and instead account for each lease component and any associated non-lease components as a single lease component.  A lessee shall not apply this practical expedient to embedded derivatives that meet the criteria in <xref id="IFRS16_X0110" base="F70459500" href="../ifrs09/IFRS09_g4.3.3-4.3.7.dita#IFRS09_g4.3.3-4.3.7/IFRS09_g4.3.3-4.3.7_TI">paragraph 4.3.3 of <ph outputclass="standard_ref"><ph outputclass="standard_number">IFRS 9</ph> <ph outputclass="standard_title">Financial Instruments</ph></ph></xref>. </p></body></paragraph>